 [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"score\": 0.9128581563449414, \"rank\": 0.0954601103848815, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Otway\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996812221, \"rank\": 3.188000255276826e-10, \"text\": \"4x100m medley relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was left frustrated following the event, with China winning gold to shatter his hopes of a sixth Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9513803894251959, \"rank\": 0.03197552826041999, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the immediate aftermath of the race, Peaty hinted he could be about to retire.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If my heart wants it, my heart wants it, and I will absolutely sign that contract with myself to do it,\\\" he s