n it comes.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just looking forward to getting home and chilling out for a bit.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the race, Peaty also took aim at China.Two members of the Chinese relay team allegedly tested positive for banned substance trimetazidine (TMZ) in the build-up to the Tokyo Games, before then being allowed to compete in 2021 after Chinese anti-doping agency claimed the substance was consumed by mistake.READ MORE:BBC cause outrage after scrapping coverage of Novak Djokovic vs Carlos Alcaraz midway through Olympic finalPeaty questioned the legitimacy of their win on Sunday, with the Olympics icon adding: \\\"One of my favourite quotes I have seen lately is that there is no point winning if you are not winning fair.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.44923631686923926, \"rank\": 0.8123040527080675, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2146, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.44923631686923926, \"rank\": 0.8123040527080675, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"